<main class="page">
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Software Engineer</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title"><span>Aaron Li</span></h1>
      <div class="hero-about">
        <div class="hero-about-block">
          <h2 class="hero-about-title">Background & interests</h2>
          <p>
            Outside of work, I spend much of my time in the gym and in the kitchen. Fitness keeps me grounded and disciplined, but cooking is where I truly slow down and enjoy the process. A routine I've recently been following is to learn a new dish every weekend to challenge myself and find new recipes I like.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-about-block">
          <h2 class="hero-about-title">Engineering expertise</h2>
          <p>
            I enjoy working on distributed systems, API design, performance optimization, and building maintainable codebases.
            I care a lot about clear abstractions, great observability, and pragmatic engineering practices that scale with a team.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section id="projects-work" class="section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Projects & Work</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="projects-work-list">
      <% @projects_work.each do |entry| %>
        <article class="card card-horizontal">
          <div class="card-media-placeholder">
            <% if entry[:image].present? %>
              <%= image_tag entry[:image], class: "card-media-image", alt: "#{entry[:title]} preview" %>
            <% else %>
              <span class="card-media-label">Work</span>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3><%= entry[:title] %></h3>
            <% if entry[:meta].is_a?(String) %>
              <p class="timeline-meta"><%= entry[:meta] %></p>
            <% end %>
            <p class="project-description"><%= entry[:description] %></p>
            <% if entry[:meta].is_a?(Array) %>
              <ul class="pill-list">
                <% entry[:meta].each do |tag| %>
                  <li class="pill"><%= tag %></li>
                <% end %>
              </ul>
            <% end %>
            <% if entry[:link].present? && entry[:link] != "#" %>
              <a href="<%= entry[:link] %>" class="card-link inline-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View project</a>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </article>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </section>
